    <h2>About the MDT Web FrontEnd</h2>
    <p>
        The MDT Web FrontEnd has been created as an easy to use, customizable and flexible solution 
        to create, access and configure the MDT Database. 
        It is a full feature replacement of the database option of the MDT Deployment Workbench.<br /><br />
        You can use it on existing MDT 2008, MDT 2008 Update 1 and MDT 2010 Databases or even create new Databases.<br /><br />
        Optionally upgrade existing Database with a lot of new helpfull features, making the handling of your daily Deployment a lot easier.<br /><br />
        Please have a look on the <a href="http://mdtwebfrontend.codeplex.com/documentation" title="MDT Web FrontEnd Documentation" target="_blank">Online Documentation</a>
        for more information.

    </p>
    
